<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-3324] NullPointerException in StreamPartitionAssignor (Kafka Streams)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-3324</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-3311&quot; title=&quot;Move co-partition checking to PartitionAssignor and auto-create internal topics&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KAFKA-3311&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KAFKA-3311&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; changed &lt;tt&gt;streams/src/main/java/org/apache/kafka/streams/processor/internals/StreamPartitionAssignor.java&lt;/tt&gt;, which  triggers NPEs consistently at this line:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;            &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; (Map.Entry&amp;lt;&lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;String&lt;/span&gt;, Set&amp;lt;TaskId&amp;gt;&amp;gt; entry : internalSourceTopicToTaskIds.entrySet()) {
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The impact is significant unfortunately because any end-to-end Streams job that I have been running keeps failing currently because of this bug.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;How to fix&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The naive fix &amp;#8211; a simple null check &amp;#8211; seems to resolve the problem.  PR incoming.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
